- Hi.</i>

06:50.201 --> 06:54.946
<i>- Hey, is anything wrong?
- No, I'm just at home, reading.</i>

06:54.956 --> 06:58.415
<i>I see. We've been trying to call you.</i>

06:58.418 --> 07:01.536
Yes, I know, but I was at a lecture.

07:01.546 --> 07:04.584
<i>Oh? What lecture?</i>

07:05.550 --> 07:10.295
<i>Biology started today. I meant
to call you back, but I was too busy.</i>

07:10.305 --> 07:12.638
Isn't that in the morning?

07:13.934 --> 07:16.597
<i>- What do you mean?
- I thought that was at eight.</i>

07:16.603 --> 07:18.595
- It's Tuesday morning, right?
- Yes.

07:19.898 --> 07:24.359
Daddy showed me how
to keep track of everything online.

07:24.361 --> 07:29.231
<i>- Well, it was moved to six just this week.
- OK.</i>

07:30.033 --> 07:33.117
But, hey, I'm cooking dinner, so...

07:33.119 --> 07:35.953
What are you making?

07:35.956 --> 07:40.542
<i>- Just some pasta and stuff.
- OK. Right.</i>

07:41.836 --> 07:46.331
<i>- But we can talk later.
- How about tomorrow?</i>

07:46.341 --> 07:48.924
<i>- Sure.
- Yes.</i>

07:48.927 --> 07:52.796
<i>- OK. We love you.
