09:37.285 --> 09:39.743
Can someone call an ambulance?

09:46.169 --> 09:48.377
Had it been a while since you ate?

09:50.465 --> 09:52.548
No, not really.

09:54.010 --> 09:56.002
Had you been drinking?

09:57.722 --> 09:59.805
Alcohol?

09:59.808 --> 10:03.472
- No, I don't really drink.
- Don't really?

10:03.478 --> 10:07.813
- No, I don't drink.
- You've never experienced it before?

10:07.816 --> 10:10.058
No.

10:10.068 --> 10:14.904
- Is it epilepsy?
- It's too early to tell.

10:14.906 --> 10:20.322
- Do you have a family history of epilepsy?
- No, not that I know of.

10:20.328 --> 10:22.866
I should look at your medical record.

10:22.872 --> 10:25.740
Can I call your family doctor back home?

10:26.835 --> 10:29.248
No, I'd rather you didn't.

10:29.254 --> 10:32.372
I don't want my parents
to know about this.

10:32.382 --> 10:36.968
They don't have to know.
I'll just talk to your doctor.

10:36.970 --> 10:39.132
It's up to you if you want to tell them.

10:40.390 --> 10:42.427
Well, OK.

10:44.144 --> 10:46.101
Could it be serious?

10:46.104 --> 10:49.643
The tests don't show anything abnormal.

10:49.649 --> 10:53.393
We'll take some more tests later on
to exclude certain conditions.

10:54.737 --> 10:57.104
Meanwhile, try not to think about it.

13:52.040 --> 13:54.032
- Hi.
- Hi.

13:55.501 --> 13:58.414
Hey, I just wanted to say hello.

13:58.421 --> 14:01.539
I was in the reading hall

14:01.549 --> 14:05.543
when you had some sort of...

14:05.553 --> 14:08.011
- Anyway, I'm Anja.
- Thelma.

14:09.474 --> 14:12.558
- But... Are you feeling better?
- Much better.

14:13.561 --> 14:15.302
Great.

14:17.940 --> 14:21.684
- Are you also studying chemistry?
- No, biology.

14:26.407 --> 14:31.368
- Good. OK, maybe I'll see you in maths.
- Yeah.

14:32.205 --> 14:34.618
- Bye.
- Bye.

15:14.622 --> 15:17.740
- It's in here.
- Here?

15:17.750 --> 15:19.491
Right.

15:45.695 --> 15:49.655
But whenever
someone mentions it, you...

15:49.657 --> 15:51.068
I don't know what you mean.

15:51.075 --> 15:55.820
- I remember Sofia and Gunnar's father.
- Aksel.

15:55.830 --> 15:59.414
Yes. Sofia and I
were going to summer camp.

15:59.417 --> 16:05.254
He started talking about how fossils were
the result of the great flood.

16:05.256 --> 16:08.715
You didn't say much,
just put an end to the conversation.

16:10.970 --> 16:13.428
Marthe's parents too, they...

16:13.431 --> 16:18.017
We met Marthe at the mall.
Was it last week?

16:18.019 --> 16:21.763
- She sends her regards.
- That's nice.

16:21.772 --> 16:23.559
They're very nice.

16:23.566 --> 16:28.311
But they believe the Earth
was created 6,000 years ago.

16:28.321 --> 16:32.110
At one time,
there was this documentary...

16:32.116 --> 16:34.403
That's enough, Thelma.

16:35.745 --> 16:38.533
Don't make fun of people.

16:40.082 --> 16:42.199
I didn't mean to, I just...

16:42.210 --> 16:44.452
Don't you agree it's strange?

16:46.214 --> 16:48.581
I'm not sure I like this new attitude.

16:49.800 --> 16:51.166
What do you mean?

16:51.177 --> 16:54.716
A little knowledge doesn't
make us better than others.

17:02.146 --> 17:05.263
How did life come to be
where there was no life?

17:08.194 --> 17:10.185
Do you know?

17:13.406 --> 17:14.897
No.

17:16.327 --> 17:18.569
You talk as if you know everything.

17:21.999 --> 17:24.036
I know I don't.

18:02.373 --> 18:04.660
- Are you feeling sad?
- Yes, a little.

18:09.714 --> 18:11.671
Want to sit here a while?

18:26.147 --> 18:28.104
What's the matter?

18:32.069 --> 18:34.061
I'm sorry, Daddy.

18:36.824 --> 18:39.908
I don't know what's wrong with me.

18:39.910 --> 18:43.745
Sometimes I think I'm better than others.

18:43.748 --> 18:45.660
And I know I'm not.

18:46.542 --> 18:49.034
But I can't help it.

18:49.045 --> 18:51.207
I'm glad you say so.

18:55.760 --> 18:57.797
Anything else?

18:59.138 --> 19:05.430
It's just when I see girls with friends and
boyfriends, they seem uglier than me.

19:05.436 --> 19:09.601
