I don't know why they...

19:14.654 --> 19:18.398
I see you're getting
new friends on Facebook.

19:18.407 --> 19:20.444
- Yes.
- Well?

19:27.375 --> 19:29.833
What's the matter?

19:29.835 --> 19:34.250
Well, I talk to some of them before lectures
and so on, but it stops there.

19:36.133 --> 19:39.251
Seems everyone knows a lot of people
already. I don't.

19:41.138 --> 19:43.095
But they have to get to know you.

19:45.559 --> 19:47.596
You're a great person.

19:50.064 --> 19:51.726
Thank you.

19:52.733 --> 19:54.690
It'll just take some time.

20:11.252 --> 20:15.713
We'll call you when we get home.
Take care.

20:15.715 --> 20:18.628
- See you soon.
- Have a nice trip.

21:51.644 --> 21:53.351
- Hi!
- Hi!

21:54.438 --> 21:56.930
How nice to see you!
Are you leaving, or...

21:56.941 --> 22:01.356
No, I was supposed to meet someone,
but it looks like they've left.

22:03.489 --> 22:05.071
- Hi.
- This is Julie.

22:05.074 --> 22:06.190
I'm Julie.

22:07.117 --> 22:09.655
Is that just a Coke?

22:10.704 --> 22:12.195
Yeah.

22:12.206 --> 22:14.744
That's it? Just a Coke?

22:14.750 --> 22:18.164
- Yeah.
- May I ask why?

22:19.255 --> 22:21.042
My family's Christian.

22:21.048 --> 22:24.587
- That's how I was raised.
- Really?

22:24.593 --> 22:27.677
Diehard Christian?
I mean, ordinary Christian?

22:28.931 --> 22:30.638
- Yeah.
- Well, that's cool.

22:33.269 --> 22:35.101
Exotic. I just...

22:35.938 --> 22:41.559
Because... Honestly,
I think that religious faith is a bit odd.

22:41.569 --> 22:46.280
"Why?"
"Well, because God or Allah..."

22:46.282 --> 22:48.524
- Or Santa Claus.
- "Santa says that's how it is."

22:48.534 --> 22:52.904
"Santa says birth control is wrong.
Let's just have 14 kids."

22:53.956 --> 22:57.791
"Santa says
women must cover their faces."

22:57.793 --> 22:59.580
I don't get it. I think it's weird.

22:59.587 --> 23:02.170
- Don't you believe in anything?
- No.

23:02.172 --> 23:08.419
Only stuff that you can explain,
that has a scientific explanation.

23:08.429 --> 23:11.342
Can you explain
how your mobile works?

23:13.934 --> 23:18.770
- Right... What do you mean?
- Well, how does it work?

23:18.772 --> 23:24.643
- It's not just because someone says so.
- Well, there are signals, like...

23:24.653 --> 23:26.690
What kind of signals?

23:26.697 --> 23:30.941
Well, it's not God. I know that for sure.

23:30.951 --> 23:33.819
But signals that are like...

23:33.829 --> 23:36.537
Help me if I'm completely...

23:36.540 --> 23:39.408
But it's in that area, like... radiation.

23:39.418 --> 23:42.035
- Radiation!
- But it is!

23:42.046 --> 23:47.587
That's why it gives you cancer.
Radiation, that's the explanation.

24:43.607 --> 24:46.350
<i>- Hi, Daddy.
- Hi.</i>

24:46.360 --> 24:48.317
Sorry for calling so late.

24:48.320 --> 24:51.063
<i>- My phone was in silent mode.
- OK.</i>

24:51.073 --> 24:53.656
<i>- Is everything OK?
- Yes.</i>

24:53.659 --> 24:55.946
<i>It's just your mother.</i>

24:55.953 --> 24:57.910
<i>She gets nervous
when you don't answer.</i>

24:57.913 --> 25:00.200
Yes, I know. Sorry.

25:00.207 --> 25:02.870
<i>She's been feeling very down again.</i>

25:02.876 --> 25:05.493
<i>She's in a lot of pain, you know.</i>

25:07.631 --> 25:09.839
<i>Where are you? Are you outside?</i>

25:10.801 --> 25:13.760
Yes. I've been out with some friends.

25:14.680 --> 25:16.797
I had a lot of fun.

25:17.808 --> 25:20.095
<i>Right.</i>

25:20.102 --> 25:23.641
<i>I'm glad you're having fun.
Just be careful.</i>

25:23.647 --> 25:25.639
I am.

25:27.151 --> 25:29.643
<i>OK. We'll talk tomorrow.</i>

25:29.653 --> 25:32.020
<i>I love you.</i>

25:32.031 --> 25:34.239
I love you too.

25:34.241 --> 25:37.655
Say hello to Mum, and tell her I'm sorry.

25:37.661 --> 25:39.653
<i>Yes, I will.</i>

25:40.706 --> 25:43.574
OK. Good night.

25:43.584 --> 25:46.372
<i>- Good night. Bye.
- Bye.</i>

28:02.681 --> 28:03.762
