28:05.684 --> 28:07.300
Hi.

28:21.366 --> 28:23.323
Thelma?

28:36.006 --> 28:38.043
Thelma?

28:39.551 --> 28:41.634
Thelma?

29:10.415 --> 29:12.577
Do you want to call someone?

29:12.584 --> 29:14.667
No, not now.

29:23.387 --> 29:25.424
I'm sorry.

29:27.766 --> 29:30.804
