- Yeah?

30:59.941 --> 31:02.524
Why did you turn up here last night?

31:02.527 --> 31:03.984
Didn't you text me?

31:05.530 --> 31:07.487
No, I don't think so.

31:15.624 --> 31:17.786
No...

31:17.793 --> 31:19.750
Did you know where I live?

31:21.671 --> 31:24.004
I must have.

31:24.007 --> 31:26.420
I've probably told you.

31:27.552 --> 31:32.422
I got pretty drunk yesterday.
I hardly remember anything.

