if you're a Christian, like.

35:05.520 --> 35:10.732
If you combine what's holy
with what's less holy.

35:10.734 --> 35:13.147
"Jesus Sa..."

35:14.029 --> 35:17.443
- What did you just say?
- "Jesus Sat..."

35:18.074 --> 35:21.533
- A little louder.
- "Jesus Satan".

35:21.536 --> 35:25.826
- Why are you whispering?
- "Jesus Satan"!

35:35.925 --> 35:37.882
You've got one there as well.

35:39.012 --> 35:42.221
I've got them everywhere.

35:44.267 --> 35:47.681
- A man?
- Yeah.

35:47.687 --> 35:50.430
The world's tiniest man.

35:50.440 --> 35:53.228
- It's nice.
- Thanks.

35:59.699 --> 36:02.692
- You OK?
- Guess I need practice.

36:02.702 --> 36:05.194
You don't have to smoke.
We can go inside.

37:08.435 --> 37:12.896
- Thank you for inviting me along.
- My pleasure.

37:12.897 --> 37:15.640
I'm glad you could make it.

37:15.650 --> 37:17.892
It's always nice to meet Anja's friends.

37:19.571 --> 37:25.192
- Have you been here before?
- No, I haven't. It's really beautiful.

37:25.201 --> 37:27.864
Let's see... I think it's this way.

37:47.724 --> 37:51.718
- Here, have a snack.
- What is it?

37:51.728 --> 37:54.971
It's one of those food bars.

37:54.981 --> 37:58.565
- I don't feel like chocolate.
- You haven't eaten.

37:59.194 --> 38:02.608
I'm OK. I don't need anything.

38:14.667 --> 38:18.377
Hey, why couldn't Daniel come?

38:18.379 --> 38:21.122
I broke up with him.

38:21.132 --> 38:25.217
- Shit! What happened?
- Don't tell Mum. She really liked him.

38:26.304 --> 38:29.797
- But are you OK?
- I'm fine.

