- Yes.</i>

43:31.734 --> 43:34.442
<i>Do you manage to get some rest
when you come home?</i>

43:35.780 --> 43:37.567
Yes.

43:38.783 --> 43:41.742
<i>Do you make dinner regularly,
or do you eat takeaway?</i>

43:42.912 --> 43:45.700
I mostly make dinner here.

43:46.916 --> 43:48.873
<i>What did you have today?</i>

43:52.380 --> 43:54.838
I made vegetable soup today.

43:58.761 --> 44:00.718
<i>Do you go shopping down there?</i>

44:02.181 --> 44:03.922
Yes.

44:07.895 --> 44:09.852
<i>What's the matter, Thelma?</i>

44:11.649 --> 44:13.606
Nothing.

44:14.360 --> 44:17.774
<i>I can always tell when there's something.</i>

44:24.745 --> 44:26.486
I...

44:28.499 --> 44:30.240
I...

44:32.837 --> 44:36.205
<i>You can always tell me, you know.
It's important that you do.</i>

44:39.010 --> 44:41.218
I've drunk alcohol.

44:42.346 --> 44:44.303
And I'm very sorry I did.

44:55.443 --> 44:57.480
<i>How much?</i>

44:59.822 --> 45:03.065
Just two beers with some friends.

45:14.420 --> 45:17.788
<i>Was that the day you didn't call us
until late in the evening?</i>

45:19.133 --> 45:20.874
Yes.

45:34.315 --> 45:36.056
<i>Right.</i>

45:38.736 --> 45:40.728
<i>Maybe it's all right.</i>

45:43.324 --> 45:46.408
<i>You're an adult now.
Need to make your own experiences.</i>

45:51.499 --> 45:53.456
<i>Maybe one beer isn't that bad.</i>

46:00.299 --> 46:03.167
<i>Just make sure you don't
lose touch with who you are.</i>

46:07.348 --> 46:09.305
No. I know.

46:10.935 --> 46:13.894
<i>- I won't.
- Many people drink too much.</i>

46:15.481 --> 46:17.438
<i>It's very easy to lose control.</i>

46:19.527 --> 46:21.314
Yes.

46:22.697 --> 46:26.065
<i>- I'm so sorry.
- It's OK.</i>

46:26.075 --> 46:28.112
<i>It's all right, Thelma.</i>

46:29.412 --> 46:33.747
<i>Don't worry about it.
I'm glad you told me.</i>

46:35.293 --> 46:38.536
<i>- Try to get some sleep.
- Yes.</i>

46:42.842 --> 46:46.210
<i>- OK, we'll talk later.
- Yes. Take care.</i>

46:46.220 --> 46:48.303
<i>- Bye.
- Bye.</i>

