It slipped my mind.

48:56.767 --> 48:59.851
Hey, sorry I had to leave.

48:59.854 --> 49:03.063
It was nice.
Tell your mum I appreciated it.

49:03.065 --> 49:05.022
I will.

49:09.738 --> 49:13.527
- Are you OK?
- Yeah. Why do you ask?

49:15.119 --> 49:16.701
Did you arrive with Kristoffer?

49:18.414 --> 49:21.077
Yeah, we came together.

49:21.792 --> 49:23.533
OK.

49:59.830 --> 50:01.162
Hey!

50:26.023 --> 50:29.016
Hey, I'm not having any.

50:29.026 --> 50:32.019
- Many of us don't smoke.
- She knows that.

50:40.162 --> 50:42.074
Sorry, count me out.

50:51.549 --> 50:53.506
Take a proper puff.

51:07.022 --> 51:09.309
Wow. Shit.

51:11.569 --> 51:14.937
- Can you feel anything?
- Maybe a bit.

51:14.947 --> 51:17.655
Yeah? Like, what?

51:20.286 --> 51:22.323
One more time.

51:27.334 --> 51:29.667
- Now I feel something.
- Yeah? Good.

51:29.670 --> 51:31.377
